# game/room.rpy:557
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7206a21e:

    # ermy_game "This thought is nothing new to me. In fact, it’s what I wake up to every single morning... I must admit it’s a rather disappointing thought, almost as much as waking up hungry."
    ermy_game "这个想法对我来并不新鲜。实际上，每个早上我一起来就会想到它……必须承认这是一个相当让人失望的想法，几乎就像饿着肚子醒来一样。"

# game/room.rpy:558
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0c6cbe2c:

    # ermy_game "Yes, hungry, as it tries to devour me day by day, to no avail. I never retaliate, yet it always stops after the first bite – I probably taste awful, like a sour grape."
    ermy_game "是的，饥饿试图吞噬我的每一天，反抗都是徒劳的，我也从不这样做，但总是在尝过一口之后就停止——因为味道尝起来很糟糕，就像一颗酸葡萄。"

# game/room.rpy:559
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a4a2a2bf:

    # ermy_game "I’ve been here, I’ve been there, I’ve been in between. I don’t believe in aliens, yet I always feel like one. Where am I supposed to be then? If only I knew... If only they knew. No one does, seriously, it’s just some people are ridiculously good at hiding the obvious."
    ermy_game "我在这里，我在那里，我介于两者之间。我不相信有外星人，但我总觉得自己是。那我应该在哪里呢?如果我知道……或是他们知道就好了。没人知道，说真的，人们太善于掩饰了。"

# game/room.rpy:560
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7c897ab3:

    # ermy_game "After some time, I decided to change my strategy and get rid of every single thought appearing in my feverish mind. Completely, entirely, eternally. After some time, I found the best solution to do so – something which I called 'mindless living', as opposed to this mindfulness nonsense, oh so popular among the masses."
    ermy_game "过了段时间后，我决定改变我的策略，摆脱每一个出现在我疯狂的脑海中的想法，完全的、全部的、永远的。这之后，我找到了最好的解决办法——我称之为\"盲目的生活\"，而不是在社会主流思想里胡言乱语。"

# game/room.rpy:561
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3f6d0e8b:

    # ermy_game "Mindless living is easy – you simply need to be dead tired all the time. I mean, when you’re exhausted, you don’t want to think, you want to sleep. In a way, I decided to go through an inverted Maslow pyramid."
    ermy_game "盲目的生存是很容易，你只需要操劳一生直到死亡就行。我的意思是，当你筋疲力尽，不想思考，而只想睡觉的那个时候。在某种程度上，这种状态就像穿过一个倒置的马斯洛金字塔 。"

# game/room.rpy:562
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_262eda81:

    # ermy_game "Strangely enough, soon my body got used to being deprived of sleep. I drastically cut down my calorie intake as a next step – this also allowed me to become quite slim, it concentrated me, one hundred percent, on food and food only, regardless of how tired I was. Meat. Fish. Pasta. Pizza. I could smell each of these words…"
    ermy_game "奇怪的是，我的身体很快地适应失眠的状态。然后我下一步大幅降低摄入的热量——这样也让我变得苗条。无论我多么困，这也让我把100％的注意力集中到食物上来。肉、鱼、意大利面、披萨，我仿佛能闻到它们的味道……"

# game/room.rpy:563
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0d361a10:

    # ermy_game "I’m not a monk or anything, so limiting myself that much became problematic – my stupid body craved sleep and food. \"Feed me! Get me some rest!\""
    ermy_game "我终究不是一个修行之人，因此控制自己变得越来越难。我愚蠢的身体想要休息与食物。\"喂饱我! 让我休息一下!\""

# game/room.rpy:564
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ca1fddb6:

    # ermy_game "Every time I succumbed to that voice of reason, I ate until I was about to blow up, and then I could sleep for a day or so, only to wake up and think…"
    ermy_game "每次当我屈服于那个想法时，我就会胡吃海喝，然后睡一整天的觉，直到醒来又开始思考。"

# game/room.rpy:565
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c645354f:

    # ermy_game "I’m not supposed to be here."
    ermy_game "我不应该在这里。"

# game/room.rpy:566
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9453a70e:

    # ermy_game "I realized I struggle that much because I probably lack training – after all, I thought, my mindless living should be treated not only as a clever invention, but also as a skill to develop. I decided to pursue a career in it, and shortly after I found my dream job. It was the number one in my shortlist – in fact, it got me enlisted."
    ermy_game "那时候我发现我之所以这么痛苦是因为自己缺少锻炼。毕竟，我想，我盲目的生存不应该只被认为是一个聪明的发现，而也应作为一种发展的技能。我下了决心在盲目生存的同时追求一份事业，过了不久，我找到了一份理想的工作。这份工作在我愿望清单中是第一名。实际上，它把我招募了。"

# game/room.rpy:567
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_1569ca4b:

    # ermy_game "Yes, I joined the army."
    ermy_game "没错，我参军了。"

# game/room.rpy:568
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_fa1459c8:

    # ermy_game "However, they fed me so well at the training camp that my silly mind decided to think again. So annoying, I’m telling you! And there was no stopping it… A phone started to ring in my head from time to time, driving me crazy. I know that as soon as I pick it up, I’d hear the same phrase…"
    ermy_game "可是，当我在军训营的时候，衣食无忧又让我的脑子开始胡思乱想了。真糟糕！一旦开始想了，就没法停止。就像电话在我脑海里响不停。我知道如果我接起这个电话，就会听到……"

# game/room.rpy:569
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c78d7157:

    # ermy_game "\"Hey! I don’t think you’re supposed to be here.\""
    ermy_game "\"嘿！我不觉得你不应该在这里。\""

# game/room.rpy:570
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_27b2a2e0:

    # ermy_game "That’s why, as soon as I could, I asked to be moved away from a grass-fed heaven of a military base to a wild, stinky battlefield."
    ermy_game "所以我尽快要求把我从和平的军训营调到狂野、恶臭的战场。"

# game/room.rpy:571
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0ad26923:

    # ermy_game "Codename Hermes, that was my new name. Have you ever heard of a soldier named Ermy? Well, me neither."
    ermy_game "我的代号是赫耳墨斯。你听说过叫叶尔米的军人吗？对了，我也没有。"

# game/room.rpy:572
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5dd606d2:

    # ermy_game "I’ve been the happiest man on planet Earth since my first deployment, but then it ended with a buzz – at least that’s what I last heard, the buzz of a bullet, before it got so dark and lonely around me."
    ermy_game "从我第一次军队部署以来，我一直认为自己是全世界最开心的人。可是，后来直到我最后听到子弹的嗡嗡声，我周围突然变得寂静黑暗。"

# game/room.rpy:573
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_bc80c965:

    # ermy_game "Darkness gave way to a white tube of light that sucked me in like a vacuum. What a strange place that was – going all the way up to somewhere above the clouds, I could’ve sworn I saw familiar faces, faces of people long gone from this world."
    ermy_game "黑暗中出现一束白色的光，它像真空一样把我吸了进去。这是一个多么奇怪的地方啊——一直走到云层之上的某个地方，我敢发誓我看到了熟悉的面孔，那些早已离开这个世界的人的面孔。"

# game/room.rpy:574
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_bedeeabc:

    # ermy_game "They looked like they wanted to tell me something, but all I could hear was that annoying buzz. Or maybe it sounded more like a distorted phone call… doesn’t matter though."
    ermy_game "他们看来想跟我说些什么，可是我所听到的只有那种让人火大的嗡嗡声。或者，它可能更像是那个熟悉的电话铃声……无所谓了。"

# game/room.rpy:575
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_4091e76b:

    # ermy_game "I don’t think I’m supposed to be here."
    ermy_game "我不应该在这里。"

# game/room.rpy:576
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7df35926:

    # ermy_game "I spent enough time in this otherwise unremarkable room, spare for a very weird note on a whiteboard."
    ermy_game "我在这个平常的房间里呆了很长时间，在白板上留了一个奇怪的便条。"

# game/room.rpy:577
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a42734e2:

    # ermy_game "To leave this room, you must tell me the answer."
    ermy_game "要离开这里，你必须给我一个答案。"

# game/room.rpy:578
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2d473ecc:

    # ermy_game "What does it mean? Who 'me'? What’s the question to begin with?"
    ermy_game "这是什么意思？‘给我’是给谁？首先，要回答的到底是什么问题？"

# game/room.rpy:579
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_993cdf82:

    # ermy_game "The only semblance of a hint came from a few more words below. Four in total: \"Love\", \"Hate\", \"Life\", \"Death\"."
    ermy_game "唯一的提示是下面写的几个词。一共有四个：\"爱情\", \"仇恨\", \"人生\", \"死亡\"。"

# game/room.rpy:580
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7594ef6b:

    # ermy_game "Well… so what of it?"
    ermy_game "所以……那又怎么样？"

# game/room.rpy:582
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ff49ed50:

    # e1 "All this makes no sense"
    e1 "所有这些都没什么意义。"

# game/room.rpy:584
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c345e091:

    # s1 "I know, dear. What is the question, I wonder? That’s what my friend and I are trying to realize."
    s1 "我知道,亲爱的。我想知道问题是什么?这就是我和我的朋友想要了解的。"

# game/room.rpy:586
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0868d950:

    # "A young woman appears seemingly out of nowhere. Dressed in an overly tight nurse uniform, she carries a syringe filled with a strange, bright liquid."
    "一个年轻的女孩子不知从什么地方冒了出来。身上穿着紧致的护士服，她拿着一支含有奇怪液体的注射器。"

# game/room.rpy:587
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_cb8159dd:

    # e1 "Who are you?"
    e1 "你是谁？"

# game/room.rpy:589
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_dcafaa9b:

    # s1 "My name is Sophie. Nice to meet you! As for my friend, he doesn’t talk much, so I’m afraid I can’t introduce him to you properly."
    s1 "我叫索菲。很高兴认识你！至于我的朋友，他不爱说话，因此恐怕无法把你正式地介绍给他。"

# game/room.rpy:591
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_aa0ed32b:

    # e1 "Your friend?"
    e1 "你的朋友？"

# game/room.rpy:593
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c8ec2342:

    # s1 "Yes, here, right in my hand. My precious friend who always knows the truth. Always but today it seems."
    s1 "对，这里，就在我的手里。我那了解真相的珍贵的朋友。今天之外，也一直都是。"

# game/room.rpy:595
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_679519ed:

    # "I thought back to my military training… The best way to deal with mentally unstable people is to take them seriously."
    "我回想了一下我的军训。对待精神状态不稳定的人最好的方法就是让他们认真起来。"

# game/room.rpy:596
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d0f3046b:

    # e1 "I guess it’s nice to have such a wise friend."
    e1 "我想有那么睿智的朋友应该还不错吧。"

# game/room.rpy:598
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_09b3c39d:

    # s1 "More like \"persistent\", I should say. It takes my friend quite some time to kick in but then there’s no stopping him, and you’re guaranteed to tell me everything I want."
    s1 "实际上，\"执著\"这个词会更合适些。我的朋友虽然需要一点时间才能开始行动，可一旦开始后就没有东西可以阻止他了。你保证会告诉我我想知道的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:602
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_31736c0e:

    # "She moves closer, and I can’t help but notice that the button on Sophie’s blouse is about to be ripped off by her… well…"
    "她走得更近了，我不由自主地注意到苏菲上衣上的纽扣就要被她扯掉了……。"

# game/room.rpy:607
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b5889205:

    # s1 "Hey darling, care to have a taste? Who knows, maybe you’re just pretending, not willing to tell me the answer… Hey, I really want to get out of this place. I don’t think I’m supposed be here."
    s1 "诶，亲爱的，想尝一尝吗？谁知道，你也许假装不愿意告诉我答案……嘿，我真想离开这儿了。我不觉得我应该在这里。"

# game/room.rpy:615
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e99bbab8:

    # m1 "Stay away, she’s clearly out of her mind."
    m1 "离她远远的， 她分明是疯了。"

# game/room.rpy:617
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_4faeb802:

    # "This room gets more crowded, now that a second girl, wrapped up in a latex costume serving presumably no other purpose rather than an aesthetic one, shows up in front of me."
    "第二个女孩儿进来后站在我前面时，房间就此刻变得更加拥挤。她穿着一套好像只为审美服务的乳胶衣服。"

# game/room.rpy:619
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f43514bc:

    # s1 "I’m much saner than you… Megan, right? At least I’m not making up a ridiculous explanation of what bound us all together here like you do."
    s1 "我比你正常多了……梅根，对吧？我至少不会为我们被限制在这里想出可笑的解释。"

# game/room.rpy:623
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c8a8866f:

    # m1 "It’s not ridiculous, it’s true. I come from an era far more advanced than yours, I know things you can’t even imagine."
    m1 "它们并不可笑的，它们都是真实的。和你的时代相比我所处的时代发达多了，所以我知道的事情你甚至不能想象。"

# game/room.rpy:627
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_58bc8214:

    # s1 "See? That’s what I’m talking about. Megan think she’s from the future."
    s1 "理解了吗？这就是我想说的。梅根觉得她来自未来。"

# game/room.rpy:631
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a148509d:

    # m1 "Still don’t believe me? Fine. What’s your last memory before you got here? I’m asking you as well, by the way. What’s your name?"
    m1 "还是不相信我吗?好吧。到这儿之前，你的最后的记忆是什么？顺便问你，你叫什么名字？"

# game/room.rpy:633
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_74f4a0d0:

    # e1 "Hermes."
    e1 "赫耳墨斯。"

# game/room.rpy:635
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_54bce0ef:

    # m1 "So, Hermes, do you remember anything?"
    m1 "所以，赫耳墨斯，你记得起来任何事情吗？"

# game/room.rpy:637
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_6652deee:

    # e1 "I heard the phone ringing somewhere very close to where I was."
    e1 "我记得听到离我很近的电话声响。"

# game/room.rpy:638
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_67b6813c:

    # "The second I say that the phone starts ringing again. Ring-ring… ring-ring… like those machines in old detective phones."
    "我说这句话的时候，电话一下子就开始响了。铃铃……铃铃……似乎就像那些老式警用电话里的铃声一样 。"

# game/room.rpy:639
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_15038066:

    # "The sound becomes more and more loud. My head hurts! Someone should stop it. Pick up the phone, please…"
    "声音越来越大。我的头疼欲裂！别让它响了，接电话，拜托……"

# game/room.rpy:641
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_24caa050:

    # m1 "What did you say?"
    m1 "你刚说什么？"

# game/room.rpy:643
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_36b25b49:

    # e1 "Can you hear it?"
    e1 "能听到吗？"

# game/room.rpy:645
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ea6891f3:

    # m1 "Hear what?"
    m1 "听到什么？"

# game/room.rpy:647
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_43daaf35:

    # e1 "That phone ringing over and over again… Jeez, it really gets on my nerves."
    e1 "电话一直响……天哪，那声音真叫我心烦。"

# game/room.rpy:649
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_abd216de:

    # m1 "My, this room must be a hangout spot for weirdos. And I thought it couldn’t be worse than when our spaceship was invaded by those creatures…"
    m1 "天哪，这个房间一定是怪人聚集的地方。我想没有比我们的太空船被那些生物入侵更坏的事了。"

# game/room.rpy:652
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_adf1fed7:

    # s1 "Please don’t mention this word again, Megan."
    s1 "请你别再说这个词，梅根。"

# game/room.rpy:656
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_80ad3d76:

    # m1 "What are you talking about?"
    m1 "你在说什么？"

# game/room.rpy:660
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c226c8fb:

    # s1 "Hang, you said… what a painful word. I was doing my daily routine, helping people to open up and talk… the guy we had back then, he just couldn’t relax, he was so nervous!"
    s1 "等一下，你说……哎呀，那么令人痛苦的词。我做我的日常工作来帮助人们敞开心扉畅所欲言……那个家伙，他一直很紧张不能放松下来！"

# game/room.rpy:661
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a9f9cb3e:

    # s1 "\"You won’t get a single word out of me!\" he shouted, rolling eyes like a madman. So silly of him! Then I heard the footsteps…"
    s1 "\"你别想从我嘴里得到一个字！\"他喊着，愚蠢地像疯子一样转着他的眼睛。那一刻我听到了脚步的声音……"

# game/room.rpy:662
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_14c1ee5f:

    # s1 "Bam! They ran out the door and barged in. \"Hey girl, nothing personal, but we don’t like to see our friend suffer. That’s a nice rope you tied him with, by the way. Why don’t we really put it to use?\""
    s1 "嘭的一下！他们从门口跑进来。\"嘿美女，抛开私人恩怨，可是我们不喜欢看到朋友受罪。对了，你把他绑住的那条绳子挺不错啊。我们为什么不好好的利用一下它呢？"

# game/room.rpy:664
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b761caf6:

    # "Sophie shivers and stops talking."
    "索菲浑身颤抖地闭嘴了。"

# game/room.rpy:666
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b319f4e8:

    # m1 "Hm… I think I just realized that, although we came from different eras, we share one thing in common."
    m1 "嗯……我觉得我才意识到，虽然咱们是来自不同的时代，我们有一个共同的东西"

# game/room.rpy:670
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e555018e:

    # n1 "Yes, yes! We’re all dead nyaw! Naomi knows what she’s talking about!"
    n1 "对对！咱们都死了，喵！娜奥米知道她在说什么！"

# game/room.rpy:672
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_475e70c9:

    # "A cute girl, dressed in a maid outfit, joins the conversation. Where was she hiding? Weird… By the way, she holds a plushie in one hand."
    "一个穿着一套女仆服的漂亮女孩儿加入对话。她之前在哪儿？奇怪……她手里拿着一个毛绒玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:674
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_50d5f946:

    # n1 "What,can’t you see it? You can, can’t you? You just don’t want to admit it… Ease up – death is the best answer-nya!"
    n1 "什么，你不能理解吗？应该能理解的啊？只是不愿意承认吧……放松！死亡就是最好的答案喵！"

# game/room.rpy:677
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0082ea6d:

    # m1 "This little brat… She keeps spouting nonsense."
    m1 "这小坏蛋……她总是胡言乱语。"

# game/room.rpy:680
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_36548f26:

    # n1 "Why, I’m just trying to play this game! Unlike you, I realized these are all answers and death is the best one of them all!"
    n1 "才不是！我只是想试着玩这个游戏！我可不像你，我早已经发现这些就是所有的答案，并且其中最好的就是死亡！"

# game/room.rpy:682
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f3906536:

    # "Ring-ring…"
    "铃铃……"

# game/room.rpy:684
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d5ff5190:

    # m1 "Death is certainly not an answer to anything, but, you know, if it helps us to get out of this place, I’m fine with it. I really need to head back home."
    m1 "死亡肯定不是答案，可是你知道 如果你能帮我们离开这里的话，我都无所谓。我真的想回家。"

# game/room.rpy:687
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f8d8e8e8:

    # n1 "No one likes the dead coming back, I’m afraid~"
    n1 "恐怕没人喜欢死人回去。"

# game/room.rpy:690
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_10edb993:

    # m1 "I’m not dead!"
    m1 "我才没死！"

# game/room.rpy:693
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a924797c:

    # s1 "I agree with Naomi… maybe death is the ultimate answer to everything. At the very least, it has the ultimate degree of certainty."
    s1 "我同意娜奥米的想法……也许死亡是一切的最终答案。至少，它具有最终的确定性。"
# game/room.rpy:696
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_6be526f0:

    # m1 "What?"
    m1 "什么？"

# game/room.rpy:699
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5da7b0a8:

    # s1 "Well, how do you know whether or not you actually live? What qualifies you as a living person?"
    s1 "我是说，你怎么知道你是否真的活着，什么使你有资格成为有生命的人？"

# game/room.rpy:702
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2cf8bddc:

    # m1 "Ridiculous. Don’t be silly. My heartbeat, for instance."
    m1 "荒唐！别犯傻了。我的心跳就可以证明。"

# game/room.rpy:705
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_20ce8586:

    # s1 "Then you compare yourself to an animal."
    s1 "那样，你就是把自己等同于动物。"

# game/room.rpy:708
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_00094163:

    # m1 "You’re getting on my nerves."
    m1 "真让我火大。"

# game/room.rpy:711
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5c42052a:

    # s1 "Hey, I’m just trying to say that, compared to the lives of some people, you’re just occupying space. On the other hand, when you die, you’re one hundred percent dead. Everyone is equal 6 feet underground. No one can challenge this fact."
    s1 "诶诶，我的意思是 和有些人的生命比起来，你活的毫无意义。不过，你一旦死了，就百分之百死了。在死亡中，人人都平等。这个毋庸置疑。"

# game/room.rpy:714
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5bfadf91:

    # m1 "Spoken like a true genius."
    m1 "你以为自己是天才吗。"

# game/room.rpy:717
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_4fa02821:

    # s1 "I know, right? I’m an underappreciated asset."
    s1 "我是啊，对吗？不要低估我的能力。"

# game/room.rpy:720
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_46461007:

    # m1 "Where are you from, again?"
    m1 "我再问一次你来自哪里？"

# game/room.rpy:723
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_84a541f5:

    # s1 "The present time."
    s1 "此刻这里。"

# game/room.rpy:726
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3c658ae3:

    # n1 "Death is the answer simply because eternal life is much worse."
    n1 "死亡是答案仅仅是因为它比永生好多了。"

# game/room.rpy:728
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d077672c:

    # e1 "Say what?"
    e1 "什么意思？"

# game/room.rpy:730
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2e89f4f4:

    # n1 "I think I still have my magic powers to show you. Kitty cat, kitty cat! Make me happy, make them sad!"
    n1 "我觉得我应该用我的魔力展示给你看。小猫，小猫！让我开心，让他们难过！"
# game/room.rpy:732
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7a29c0fd:

    # "I’m quite sure she’s referring to that plushie."
    "我很确定她指的是那个毛绒玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:734
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_70808d71:

    # e1 "Um, so what’s going to happen now?"
    e1 "嗯，现在会发生什么事情？"

# game/room.rpy:736
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9dacbfe4:

    # n1 "Eternity!"
    n1 "永恒！"

# game/room.rpy:738
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_1339ec42:

    # e1 "What do you mean?"
    e1 "什么意思？"

# game/room.rpy:740
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_136d5ffa:

    # n1 "Time will go, but we won’t follow!"
    n1 "时间会过去，但我们不会跟随！"

# game/room.rpy:742
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0ae46a18:

    # "And she was right."
    "原来，她是对的。"

# game/room.rpy:776
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_1db227a2:

    # s1 "What day is it today?"
    s1 "今天是周几？"

# game/room.rpy:779
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_60e4a148:

    # n1 "Friday-nya!"
    n1 "周五喵！"

# game/room.rpy:782
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9e96918a:

    # m1 "Jeez, how would you know? Thanks for your trick, time lost its meaning."
    m1 "天哪，你怎么知道的呀？感谢你的把戏，现在时间失去意义了。"

# game/room.rpy:785
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_976d7936:

    # n1 "Therefore, it might as well always be Friday?"
    n1 "所以，也许总是周五？"

# game/room.rpy:788
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d1fc1a68:

    # m1 "It’s been what… days, months, years?"
    m1 "已经过了好几……天、月还是年？"

# game/room.rpy:791
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_391c93e5:

    # s1 "Hey Naomi, can you revert your spell?"
    s1 "嗨，娜奥米，你能把你的魔咒取消吗？"

# game/room.rpy:794
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b80c981a:

    # n1 "Tee-hee… if you all admit death is the answer, maybe I could!"
    n1 "嘻嘻……要是你们愿意承认死亡是答案，我也许可以考虑！"

# game/room.rpy:797
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b8404223:

    # s1 "Okay, I admit it."
    s1 "好吧，我承认。"

# game/room.rpy:800
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e55242c7:

    # m1 "No way I’m going to fall for this trick. You want to stay here forever? Fine, let’s talk. Little by little, the future will come, and that’s exactly where I’m from."
    m1 "我不会上你的当！你们想永远都在这儿吗？没问题，让我们聊一下。未来一定会慢慢到来，而那正是我来的地方。"

# game/room.rpy:803
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8cdca407:

    # n1 "Okay! Let’s talk about cats."
    n1 "好吧！让我们谈谈小猫。"

