    # n1 "Let’s talk about foals."
    n1 "让我们谈谈小马驹。"

# game/room.rpy:840
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_15658208:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about foxes."
    n1 "让我们谈谈狐狸。"

# game/room.rpy:844
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8805db41:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about forests."
    n1 "让我们谈谈森林。"

# game/room.rpy:848
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_39de2463:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fonts."
    n1 "让我们谈谈字体。"

# game/room.rpy:853
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d5add85d:

    # m1 "Stop it! I can’t take it anymore!"
    m1 "够了！我受不了了！"

# game/room.rpy:855
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0f435484:

    # m1 "Fine, maybe death is the answer. Whatever…"
    m1 "好的，死亡是答案。算了……"

# game/room.rpy:857
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5014debd:

    # "I too agreed with that. However, nothing happened."
    "我也同意，但是，什么都没发生。"

# game/room.rpy:858
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a5497450:

    # e1 "Uh, what’s next? What should we do?"
    e1 "嗯……下一步是什么？ 我们应该做什么？"

# game/room.rpy:860
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3d74f157:

    # s1 "I think we should be more proactive, now that we all agree on our answer. See this purple liquid? It’s the last resort liquid, so to speak. Let me help you, friends…"
    s1 "我觉得一旦咱们都同意了，就该更加积极主动。大家能看到这个紫色的液体了吗？这是最后一个了。让我帮你们一下，朋友们……"

# game/room.rpy:861
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_55b44aa5:

    # "She moves so swiftly. It doesn’t even hurt… My vision starts to become blurry."
    "她迅速行动起来。还没感到疼痛，我的眼前就变得模糊起来。"

# game/room.rpy:863
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a75c52f6:

    # "Ring-ring. The phone rings again, but this time I manage to answer it, somehow."
    "叮铃铃。电话再次响起，但是这次我设法接起电话。"

# game/room.rpy:864
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_84e76fe8:

    # "The guy on the other end of the line tells me that if I die, I’ll stay in this room forever. Uhm… why haven’t I thought about it before?"
    "电话那头的家伙跟我说要是我死亡，就会永远留在这个房间里。哼……我怎么之前没想到呢？"

# game/room.rpy:865
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5833a61e:

    # "I’m afraid it’s too late now."
    "恐怕现在已经太晚了。"

# game/room.rpy:867
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_6cafbc94:

    # "\"Love\""
    "\"爱情\""

# game/room.rpy:868
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d2faa229:

    # e1 "Love? What is love?"
    e1 "爱情？爱情是什么？"

# game/room.rpy:870
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_4d464fd2:

    # n1 "Baby don’t hurt me… oh, pardon me! Hi! What would your order be?"
    n1 "宝贝别伤到我……哦，对不起！嗨！您要点什么？"
# game/room.rpy:871
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_95474de9:

    # e1 "Naomi? You’re… alive?"
    e1 "娜奥米？你……活着吗？"

# game/room.rpy:873
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_59914448:

    # n1 "Yes, why? However, I woke up in this room today. You know, that milk tea I had yesterday… it tasted so weird. Anyway, although it’s not my tavern anymore , I certainly have a customer."
    n1 "当然，怎么了？可是，我今天在这个房间醒来了。你知道，昨天的那杯奶茶……味道好奇怪。反正，虽然这里不是我的酒馆，但我肯定会有个客人。"

# game/room.rpy:874
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_84a1e791:

    # e1 "What can I order?"
    e1 "我可以点什么菜？"

# game/room.rpy:876
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e20e6c41:

    # n1 "Nothing, I’m afraid. We’re short on everything. But I can make you company! I’m a good maid, after all."
    n1 "恐怕什么都不可以。我们什么都没有。但是，我可以陪你！毕竟我是个女仆。"

# game/room.rpy:877
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b1a80b2d:

    # e1 "Did you see this strange whiteboard?"
    e1 "你有看到那个奇怪的白板吗？"

# game/room.rpy:879
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c2949f2c:

    # n1 "Sure I did! What do you think the answer is-nya?"
    n1 "当然！你觉得答案是什么喵？"

# game/room.rpy:880
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5b3ee10e:

    # e1 "Love."
    e1 "爱情。"

# game/room.rpy:882
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_51562a0a:

    # n1 "How romantic of you! Sadly, I know nothing of it. I’m not allowed to get into an affair with a customer, even with one as handsome as you. However… let my magic do the work and say whether or not you’re right-nya! Kitty cat, kitty cat, make me happy, make them sad!"
    n1 "你真浪漫！很可惜我对爱情不了解。我不被允许和客人交往，即使客人像你这么帅。不过……让我使用我的魔力确认你是对的还是错的喵！小猫小猫!让我开心让他们难过！"

# game/room.rpy:883
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_6f62cd52:

    # "Two other girls appear right in front of my eyes."
    "两个其他的女孩子突然出现就在我眼前。"

# game/room.rpy:887
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8551e79d:

    # n1 "Tell me, what is love?"
    n1 "告诉我，爱情是什么？"

# game/room.rpy:890
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3ffa9ff9:

    # m1 "Love is reducible to the absurd act of chemicals. Therefore, there is no intrinsic value in this material universe."
    m1 "爱情可以说是一种荒谬的化学反应。因此，它在这个物质世界没什么固有价值。"

# game/room.rpy:893
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_31306ef3:

    # s1 "Hypocrite that you are, for you trust the chemicals in your brain to tell you they are chemicals. All knowledge is ultimately based on that which we cannot prove. Will you fight? Or will you perish like a dog?"
    s1 "你好虚伪，因为你相信你脑子里的化学物质跟你说它就是化学物质。所有的知识都建立在我们无法证明的基础上。你要反抗吗？还是要像个狗一样死掉呢？"

# game/room.rpy:896
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7a418a0b:

    # n1 "Sorry, they’re a bit broken. Let me fix it-nya!"
    n1 "对不起，她们坏了一点点。我来修一下喵！"

# game/room.rpy:904
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8551e79d_1:

    # n1 "Tell me, what is love?"
    n1 "告诉我，爱情是什么？"

# game/room.rpy:905
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_6974623a:

    # "Silence was her answer."
    "沉默是她的答案。"

# game/room.rpy:907
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ba59fce4:

    # n1 "Oh my, oh my, still no good. Well, let me try this little trick! In a second, they’re going to fall for you, Hermes!"
    n1 "天哪，还不行。让我试一下这个小把戏！一瞬间她们就会爱上你了，赫耳墨斯！"

# game/room.rpy:909
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3d645029:

    # "She spanks me with her plushie."
    "她用她的玩具打我的屁股。"

# game/room.rpy:911
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_abcbdcc3:

    # "I notice Sophie and Megan staring at me."
    "我发现索菲和梅根盯着我看。"

# game/room.rpy:913
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_1a883a9b:

    # m1 "Um, Hermes?"
    m1 "嗯……赫耳墨斯？"

# game/room.rpy:914
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e728d812:

    # e1 "Yes?"
    e1 "嗯？"

# game/room.rpy:916
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_da584911:

    # m1 "I… I love you."
    m1 "我……我爱你。"

# game/room.rpy:917
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_190fa817:

    # e1 "Why?"
    e1 "为什么？"

# game/room.rpy:919
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e0b9e159:

    # m1 "Should I have a reason?"
    m1 "还要原因吗？"

# game/room.rpy:920
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ca4c5a22:

    # e1 "No, but I’m curious."
    e1 "不要，就是好奇。"

# game/room.rpy:922
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_cd0d4e7a:

    # m1 "Just because you’re here."
    m1 "只是因为你在这儿。"

# game/room.rpy:923
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9a0c13f9:

    # e1 "I’ve been here before."
    e1 "我以前来过啊。"

# game/room.rpy:925
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d1545791:

    # m1 "Really? Well, people change, don’t they?"
    m1 "真的吗？哼……人们总是在改变，对吧？"

# game/room.rpy:928
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5188dce6:

    # s1 "He’s mine! He will be my darling. Only you and I forever more, Hermes."
    s1 "他是我的！他要当我亲爱的。只有你和我，永远在一起，赫耳墨斯。"

# game/room.rpy:929
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ce95f0e8:

    # e1 "Hey, we’re kind of stuck here together."
    e1 "嗨，我们一起陷在这里了。"

# game/room.rpy:932
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_63d0fcdd:

    # n1 "But if you could leave… which one of them would you choose to go with you-nya?"
    n1 "但是，要是你能离开……想她们其中哪个跟你一起走呢喵？"

# game/room.rpy:936
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5db9a200:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "你行为好奇怪。这些名字我都不认识。"

# game/room.rpy:939
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5db9a200_1:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "你行为好奇怪。这些名字我都不认识。"

# game/room.rpy:942
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5db9a200_2:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "你行为好奇怪。这些名字我都不认识。"

# game/room.rpy:945
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b7057560:

    # m1 "It hurts me that you’d think of other girls during a moment like this."
    m1 "你这种时刻还会想着其他的女孩子真让我感到伤心。"

# game/room.rpy:948
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_94d97829:

    # s1 "Yeah, how could you? It’s so selfish… from another side, love is the most selfish feeling anyway."
    s1 "对吧，你怎么能这么做？那么自私……可是，从另一个角度看，爱情是世界上最自私的感情。"

# game/room.rpy:950
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2f5d78a1:

    # e1 "What?"
    e1 "什么意思？"

# game/room.rpy:952
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d4d70ff8:

    # s1 "Selfish, of course, if it’s not eternal… and what is eternal love? Eternal love means you should stay together until the very end. Till death do us part!"
    s1 "当然如果爱情不是永恒的，那就是自私的……永恒的爱情是什么？永恒的爱情意味着你们一直都要在一起。直至死亡将你们分开！"

# game/room.rpy:954
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_98b90bd4:

    # s1 "Now, I’m sure that after some time you’re definitely going to choose me over anyone else. The question is, how can I be sure that your feeling lasts forever?"
    s1 "现在呢，我完全确定过一会你一定会选择我，可是问题是我怎么来保证你的爱情会始终如一？"

# game/room.rpy:957
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_114a833d:

    # m1 "What are you talking about? Stop babbling nonsense."
    m1 "你在说什么？别胡说了。"

# game/room.rpy:960
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_98e9d238:

    # s1 "Trust me, my words make perfect sense. Here, let my friend explain this to you."
    s1 "相信我，我说的十分有道理。我的朋友来给你解释。"

# game/room.rpy:965
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_c62123ff:

    # "She does a few quick swings, and shortly after that we’re the only ones standing in the room."
   "她快速走了几步，不久之后，我们是唯一站在房间里的人。"

# game/room.rpy:966
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_75b83749:

    # e1 "W-what have you done? How could you?"
    e1 "你做了什么？你怎么能？"

# game/room.rpy:968
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_011582e6:

    # s1 "Same as you, I’m just being selfish. All fair and square! Fair… you know what? Love is not the answer. Love is not fair."
    s1 "和你一样，我就是自私的。公平而公正！公正……你知道么?爱情不是答案。爱情并不公正。"

# game/room.rpy:970
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_4de88049:

    # "I feel cold sweat dripping down my back. Sophie’s clearly bonkers, and I need to calm her down somehow."
    "我感觉到背后一阵冷汗。索菲显然是疯子，我需要让她平静下来。"

# game/room.rpy:971
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_fecabd29:

    # e1 "Not fair? But why? I always thought love is one of the best feelings in the world."
    e1 "不公正吗？这为什么？我一直都觉得爱情是世界上最好的感情之一。"

# game/room.rpy:973
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f3bb75fb:

    # s1 "I never said it’s bad, I said it’s not fair. Love should be mutual, but it never works that way."
    s1 "我没说它不好，而是说它不公正。爱情该是相互的，可它从来不这样。"

# game/room.rpy:975
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_61d98b07:

    # s1 "Remember, Hermes, between two people involved, one loves while the other allows himself or herself to be loved. How is this fair?"
    s1 "要记得，赫耳墨斯，两个人里其中一个人是爱对方的，而另一个就让自己被爱着。这怎么公平呢？"

# game/room.rpy:977
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a8cb72eb:

    # e1 "I don’t believe you."
    e1 "我不相信你。"

# game/room.rpy:979
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b3c2b8c9:

    # s1 "Oh, and love is also very selfish, remember? Even more selfish than you and me."
    s1 "再说，爱情总是很自私，还记得吗？比我和你还自私。"

# game/room.rpy:981
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_dc7a5c78:

    # e1 "What about love you have for your parents?"
    e1"你对父母的爱呢？"

# game/room.rpy:983
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ed3c846a:

    # s1 "It all goes down the same street. Every time you buy them something, you feel like a good kid. In a way, you buy it for yourself, Hermes... Now, what I’m going to do is to have you all for myself."
    s1 "一样的。你每次给他们买东西，都会觉得自己是好孩子。在一定程度上，你是为了自己而买那些东西，赫耳墨斯。现在，我要做的就是让大家珍惜自己。"

# game/room.rpy:984
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8af92fc8:

    # "Swing! The needle bites me like a snake. My legs start to tremble."
    "针就像蛇一样咬住我。我的腿开始发抖。"

# game/room.rpy:986
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_476cf9b6:

    # s1 "It feels so… satisfying!"
    s1 "感觉那么……令人满意。"

# game/room.rpy:988
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ae199ff2:

    # "Sophie’s face is the last thing to flash in my mind before darkness covers everything around me."
    "黑暗席卷我之前，索菲的脸是我最后看到的影像。"

# game/room.rpy:994
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_80661c14:

    # "I’m back from the dead, it seems. Even more, the usual crowd’s here, as if nothing happened at all. The phone starts ringing again."
    "看来我复活了。这几个人也都在，似乎什么都没发生。电话又响起来了。"

# game/room.rpy:995
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e0285bd8:

    # "I don’t think I can get rid of that pain in my head, so I badly need to concentrate on something else… maybe small talk can help."
    "我头疼不止，所以我非常需要转移注意力……聊天也许能有帮助。"

# game/room.rpy:996
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_598cb488:

    # e1 "Hey, do you guys remember what just happened?"
    e1 "嗨，大家，你们记得刚刚发生什么事情了么？"

# game/room.rpy:998
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3bad760e:

    # m1 "Um, nothing yet? We have to find the answer, and…"
    m1 "嗯，目前没什么？我们得想出对的答案，然后……"

# game/room.rpy:1001
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0bf62620:

    # n1 "And I’m sure the answer is one of these words-nya!"
    n1 "我确定答案是这些词语其中之一喵！"

# game/room.rpy:1003
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_02f3e9ea:

    # "You’re kidding me. Have they entirely forgotten about what happened before?"
    "你一定是在开玩笑。她们难道把所有之前发生的事情都忘了吗？"

# game/room.rpy:1005
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_fba2a399:

    # s1 "Hm… which word would it be?"
    s1 "哼……你想的是哪一个词？"

# game/room.rpy:1008
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_630b973a:

    # n1 "Easy… Hate! Hate is the answer!"
    n1 "很简单……仇恨！答案肯定是仇恨！"

# game/room.rpy:1011
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_15b26fae:

    # s1 "Why do you think so?"
    s1 "你为什么这么想？"

# game/room.rpy:1014
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9b3d3d1b:

    # n1 "Well, I hate you all, so this word is definitely a suitable answer for me. "
    n1 "你看 我恨你们所有人，因此对我来说，这个答案是最合适的。"

# game/room.rpy:1017
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_1adc9e55:

    # m1 "For you, yes, for me, no."
    m1 "对你来说是，对我不是。"

# game/room.rpy:1020
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0aee5c79:

    # n1 "But why would I care about you-nya?"
    n1 "可是我为什么要在意你们呢喵？"

# game/room.rpy:1023
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_17c8dc61:

    # s1 "I wonder what’s your reason for hating us that much."
    s1 "我也想知道，你那么恨我们的原因是什么。"

# game/room.rpy:1026
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_32f53bf8:

    # n1 "It’s simple, you know-nya… I hate you because you leave me no hope."
    n1 "很简答 你知道喵……因为你们不给我希望，所以我恨你们。"

# game/room.rpy:1029
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e6d2010d:

    # s1 "Why, I wonder?"
    s1 "为什么，我想知道？"

# game/room.rpy:1032
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_32411d59:

    # n1 "If you’re right and I came from the past, then I see my future in the two of you. What can I say? This future looks pathetic…"
    n1 "如果你是对的，我来自过去，那么我会在你们两个中看到我的未来。我还能说什么？这种未来看起来很可悲……"

# game/room.rpy:1035
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_83e47828:

    # m1 "But you don’t know us at all."
    m1 "可是你根本不理解我们。"

# game/room.rpy:1038
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f8f12659:

    # n1 "Even five minutes is enough. I despise you."
    n1 "五分钟就够了。我鄙视你们。"

# game/room.rpy:1040
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8e2bb17a:

    # "Her annoyance doesn’t seem to be justified at the very slightest, but I’m not surprised, as it fits perfectly with the weird ambiance of that place."
    "她的生气看来一点道理也没有，可我并不吃惊。这正好符合这个地方古怪的气氛。"

# game/room.rpy:1042
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b0648637:

    # s1 "I don’t think hate is the answer because it’s too easy to hate something."
    s1 "我觉得仇恨是答案的可能性不大，因为恨某个东西总是太容易了。"

# game/room.rpy:1044
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f877b003:

    # e1 "And who said the answer should be complicated?"
    e1 "谁说答案一定要复杂呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1046
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_decd0964:

    # s1 "What do you hate, Hermes?"
    s1 "你最恨什么，赫耳墨斯？"

# game/room.rpy:1048
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_852a002a:

    # e1 "Other people."
    e1 "别人。"

# game/room.rpy:1050
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_552b1ac7:

    # s1 "Including me?"
    s1 "包括我吗？"

# game/room.rpy:1052
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d3978f51:

    # e1 "We just met, but I’m sure I’m capable of developing a whole nanoangstrom of hate directed towards you."
    e1 "我们刚刚见面，可是我确定有一天会很恨你。"

# game/room.rpy:1054
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d1423817:

    # s1 "Why?"
    s1 "为什么？"

# game/room.rpy:1057
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b93fe669:

    # m1 "Yeah, why?"
    m1 "对啊，为什么呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1059
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d256d946:

    # e1 "Because you make me feel like I’m not supposed to be here."
    e1 "因为你让我感到我不应该在这里。"

# game/room.rpy:1061
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ae425021:

    # m1 "What would’ve changed had we not existed at all?"
    m1 "如果我们根本不存在会有什么改变 ？"

# game/room.rpy:1064
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e6ce7e7b:

    # n1 "Then he couldn’t compare. If he had no other place to be, his thought would become invalid. I agree with you, Hermes. If I hadn’t seen the future right before my eyes, I’d have been fine with everything."
    n1 "那他就无从比较。如果他没有其他地方可以去，他的想法就没有意义。我同意你的看法，赫耳墨斯。要是我没有亲眼看到未来，我会觉得怎样都可以。"

# game/room.rpy:1067
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3d61b9c5:

    # s1 "You guys don’t even know about the right reason to hate everyone around you. I mean… they exist. They smell, they take space, they’re loud and annoying. That’s why I always stay in my lab, so I could have some personal space. But even there, when I visit the bathroom, I look in the mirror and realize I’m no different."
    s1 "你们甚至找不到恨周围每个人的正当理由。我是说……他们存在、他们呼吸、占用空间、他们吵到让人心烦。这就是为什么我一直待在实验室里的原因，这里我可以有一些私人空间。但是即使在这儿，每当我去洗手间时，我看着镜子里的自己意识到自己没有什么不同。"# game/room.rpy:1069
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f6bf548f:

    # e1 "What about you, Megan?"
    e1 "你呢，梅根？"

# game/room.rpy:1071
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7fd3821b:

    # m1 "I don’t know. In the future, our personalities are removed as they serve little to no purpose. We don’t live, we function. I still have some emotions but hate is too strong, it’s off limits."
    m1 "我不知道。将来我们的个性都将被删除，因为它们几乎没有用处。我们不是活着，是指单纯地发挥作用。我仍然会有些情绪，但是仇恨感太强烈了，这是不可以的。"

# game/room.rpy:1078
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_550e2853:

    # n1 "Hermes! Hi-nya! Finally, it’s only me and you here!"
    n1 "赫耳墨斯！嗨喵！终于只剩咱们两个人了！"

# game/room.rpy:1080
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f887d2da:

    # e1 "Where has everyone else gone?"
    e1 "其他人去哪儿了？"

# game/room.rpy:1082
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_bfd62e5b:

    # n1 "What makes you think they’ve ever been here to begin with?"
    n1 "是什么让你认为他们曾经来过这里？"

# game/room.rpy:1084
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_97e6d0a1:

    # n1 "Anyway… I’m here to support you-nya! Trust me, hate is not the answer! Life, yes, life is!"
    n1 "反正……我是支持你的喵！相信我，仇恨不是答案！生活才是！"

# game/room.rpy:1086
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_432f24e4:

    # n1 "I want you to know that you’re supposed to be here with me. Stay with me forever, Hermes."
    n1 "我想让你知道你应该和我一起在这里。永远和我在一起吧，赫耳墨斯。"

# game/room.rpy:1087
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2c13b61e:

    # e1 "Why are you so sure about it?"
    e1 "你怎么那么确定？"

# game/room.rpy:1089
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0f6fd17d:

    # n1 "Because I don’t think this place was supposed to exist in the first place. It feels made up. Therefore, you fit in perfectly. Think of it as a new life for both of us."
    n1 "因为我觉得这个地方不应该存在。它是虚构的。你却正好适合在这里。我们可以在这里开始我们两个的新生活。"

# game/room.rpy:1090
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_fe6e732f:

    # e1 "Life… you think life is the answer?"
    e1 "生活……你认为生活是答案吗？"

# game/room.rpy:1092
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_577273e1:

    # n1 "Yes, because I want to spend my life with you."
    n1 "是的，因为我想与你共度此生。"

# game/room.rpy:1093
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_57d2f7bf:

    # e1 "What… what are we going to do?"
    e1 "咱……咱们要做什么？"

# game/room.rpy:1095
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_684cb5b8:

    # n1 "Everything but one thing… we’ll never walk alone. And… you know, I’m a maid. I can always serve you a cup of tea when you need it. Trust me, having a friend like this is what matters the most."
    n1 "除了一件事之外都可以……咱们永远不会孤独。还有……你知道 我是女仆。要是你需要，我总能给你泡一杯茶。相信我，有这种朋友才是最重要的。"

# game/room.rpy:1096
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e8238865:

    # e1 "Thanks, Naomi… I-I don’t even know what to say."
    e1 "谢谢娜奥米……我——我甚至不知道说什么。"

# game/room.rpy:1098
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_072f1189:

    # s1 "It’s because you actually want to spend your whole life with me instead, you know."
    s1 "这也许是因为你确实想与我共度此生，而不是她？"

# game/room.rpy:1099
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8faeaea5:

    # e1 "Hey, where did Naomi go?"
    e1 "诶，娜奥米又去哪儿呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1101
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_791c8d49:

    # s1 "It doesn’t matter. It’s just you and I here now, Hermes. You and I."
    s1 "这不重要。现在只有你和我两个人了，赫耳墨斯。你和我。"

# game/room.rpy:1102
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_14657251:

    # e1 "What are we going to do?"
    e1 "咱们要做什么呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1104
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5e6d7832:

    # s1 "We’re going to have some fun, you know. Admit it, that’s what you really want. Everything else is just a façade to mask your desire."
    s1 "我们会玩得很开心的 。承认吧，这就是你真正想要的。其他的一切只是掩饰你这个欲望的面具。"

# game/room.rpy:1105
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a7246076:

    # e1 "T-that’s not true…"
    e1 "才——才不是……"

# game/room.rpy:1107
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0dba7c36:

    # s1 "Well, do you want my friend to ask you this question again? He’ll get an honest answer out of you."
    s1 "哼……你想我的朋友再次问你这个问题吗？他肯定会从你那里得到诚实的答案。"

# game/room.rpy:1108
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_dd9803ce:

    # e1 "T-there’s no need for that…"
    e1 "没——没有必要……"

# game/room.rpy:1110
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_e31fba8a:

    # s1 "See? Now you’re being frank. Don’t worry, it’s okay. Think of yourself as a part of a hunter-gatherer world, it will make your life a whole lot easier. It’s just you, the things you own and the things you want to own."
    s1 "看到了吧。现在你很坦白。不用担心，一切都好。你可以试想自己是世界的一部分，这样你的生活会变得轻松多了。生活中只有你自己，你拥有的东西和你想要拥有的东西。"

# game/room.rpy:1111
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f6c62981:

    # e1 "But I don’t want to think of you as a thing."
    e1 "可是我不想把你看做一个东西。"

# game/room.rpy:1113
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8c9c6948:

    # s1 "Well then, someone else would, my dear, and you’d be surprised about the choice I make."
    s1 "好吧，其他人会的，亲爱的，你会对我的选择感到惊讶。"
# game/room.rpy:1114
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_cedbf49f:

    # e1 "Life is not as primitive as you portray it."
    e1 "生活不像你描绘的那么原始 。"

# game/room.rpy:1116
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_35f42b63:

    # s1 "Life works the way you make it work, simple as that. I want my life to be primitive, so here I am. You know why you feel like you’re not supposed to be here? Because you don’t even know what kind of life you want to live."
    s1 "生活就是按照你的方式运作的，就这么简单。我认为生活是原始的，所以我在这里。你知道你为什么觉得你不应该在这里吗？因为你甚至不知道自己想过什么样的生活。"

# game/room.rpy:1117
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_cb55d00a:

    # e1 "I… well…"
    e1 "我……嗯……"

# game/room.rpy:1119
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_6c2834b6:

    # s1 "Don’t worry, Hermes. Let me take care of it. Let me comfort you, my dear, so you could forget about everything else."
    s1 "没关系的，赫耳墨斯。让我替你处理这件事。让我来安慰你，亲爱的，以便你可以忘记其他的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:1121
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5615a6d3:

    # m1 "No way!"
    m1 "不可能吧！"

# game/room.rpy:1122
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d4ed5509:

    # e1 "Hey, what just happened? Where did Sophie go?"
    e1 "嗨，刚刚发生什么事情？索菲又去哪儿呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1124
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f8af7a15:

    # m1 "I got rid of that succubus."
    m1 "我摆脱了那个女妖。"

# game/room.rpy:1126
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5be7b092:

    # m1 "Hey, stay with me, Hermes. I’ve seen the future, and it’s not the best one, I admit… now we’ll have a second chance to make it great."
    m1 "诶，你跟我一起吧，赫耳墨斯。我承认，我看到了未来，但这不是最好的未来。现在，我们将有另一次机会来实现美好的未来。"

# game/room.rpy:1127
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_14657251_1:

    # e1 "What are we going to do?"
    e1 "咱们要做什么？"

# game/room.rpy:1129
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_b5e504d0:

    # m1 "We’re going to believe in tomorrow. If you think you’re not supposed to be here, make tomorrow the place to be. Please… do it for me"
    m1 "咱们要相信明天。要是你认为你不应该在这里，那就去你心中的明天。拜托……就算为了我。"

# game/room.rpy:1131
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_f9c9172a:

    # e1 "Will you love me?"
    e1 "你会爱我吗？"

# game/room.rpy:1133
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_17a917c3:

    # m1 "I’ll love the you of tomorrow, I promise."
    m1 "我保证我一定会爱明天的你。"

# game/room.rpy:1135
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5cf9fa4c:

    # "I try to push the button, but nothing happens. Maybe I should try tomorrow."
    "我尝试按下按钮，可是什么都没有发生。我也许应该明天再次试一下。"

# game/room.rpy:1140
translate chinese close_game_02a0c651:

    # "Okay, I had enough... I should think of a proper way to give feedback on this masterpiece."
    "好吧，我受够了……我应该想出一种适当的方式来反馈这部杰作。"

# game/room.rpy:1146
translate chinese close_game_done_5cf9fa4c:

    # "I try to push the button, but nothing happens. Maybe I should try tomorrow."
    "我尝试按下按钮，可是什么都没发生。我也许应该明天再尝试一下。"

# game/room.rpy:1165
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_3aae40ef:

    # "Man, I'm beat."
    "天哪，我被打败了。"

# game/room.rpy:1166
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_a73a474b:

    # "My mind still goes over what I heard on the way home."
    "我脑海中还是在考虑回家的路上听到的那句话。"

# game/room.rpy:1167
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_128fa27b:

    # "Never judge the book by its cover, right?"
    "永远不要以貌取人，是吧？"

# game/room.rpy:1168
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_eca482cd:

    # "Should I give Ermy's game another go?"
    "我要不要再次试着玩叶尔米的游戏呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1169
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_dc694895:

    # "But first, let me check on my sister."
    "可是要先看看我的妹妹。"

# game/room.rpy:1171
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_68718e2a:

    # "I can't believe you came empty-handed again."
    "我简直不敢相信你又空手来了。"

# game/room.rpy:1172
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_ba2a844e:

    # "That girl from yesterday came again, saying she needs to check on your progress."
    "昨天来过的那个女孩子今天又来了，说她需要查一下你的进度。"

# game/room.rpy:1173
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_0cb9b9cc:

    # "I replied that you can handle everything yourself."
    "我跟她说你能够自己处理所有的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:1174
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_adfabd92:

    # "By the way, what was in that document she gave you?"
    "对了，她给你的纸卷是什么？"

# game/room.rpy:1177
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_84ec55af:

    # "Honestly, I forgot about that strange, pixelated thing."
    "实话说，我完全忘了还有那个奇怪的像素化的东西。"

# game/room.rpy:1180
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_100c76d5:

    # "Hm... Is it a bit different today? Just my imagination, probably."
    "嗯……今天它看起来不一样了，是不是？可能只是我想象的。"

# game/room.rpy:1186
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_bc966201:

    # nvl clear
    # nvl_narrator "Nothing again, nothing, how, impossible, halfway done, nothing, no, screw it."
    nvl clear
    nvl_narrator "再也没有，什么也没有，怎么做，不可能，完成一半，什么都没有，没有，糟了。"

# game/room.rpy:1188
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_4cd515b7:

    # nvl_narrator "We need to be more creative, numbers, letter, numbers, letters, boring, boring."
    nvl_narrator "我们需要更具创造力，数字，字母，数字，字母，无聊，无聊。"

# game/room.rpy:1189
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_3000c02c:

    # nvl_narrator "New setting again, this time we will make it, I'm telling you."
    nvl_narrator "有新的背景了，这次一定会成功的 我告诉你。"

# game/room.rpy:1190
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_d5032d4f:

    # nvl_narrator "New everything, no boring stuff, music, yes, music, music, love."
    nvl_narrator "一切都新的，没有无聊东西，音乐，对，音乐，音乐，爱情。"

# game/room.rpy:1191
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_f549e11c:

    # nvl_narrator "Empathy, empathy, affection, we need to show it, please, please help me"
    nvl_narrator "同情，同情，喜爱，我们要把它们表现清楚，拜托，拜托帮助我。"

# game/room.rpy:1192
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_fafcaa21:

    # "{nw}"
    "{nw}"

# game/room.rpy:1195
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_7dc3beab:

    # "Same as yesterday... Who on earth writes this nonsense?"
    "与昨天一样……究竟谁会写这些没有意义的东西？"

# game/room.rpy:1198
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_e34cee22:

    # "Alright, time for Ermy's masterpiece."
    "好吧，体验叶尔米的杰作时间到了。"

# game/room.rpy:1224
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_5526f512:

    # nvl clear
    # ermy_game "I’m in this room again, the girls staring at me, awaiting eagerly what’s going to happen next."
    nvl clear
    ermy_game "我又在这个房间里，女孩子们盯着看我，热切盼望着接下来会发生什么事情。"

# game/room.rpy:1226
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_d7cdef92:

    # ermy_game "Well, truth is… Nothing’s going to happen."
    ermy_game "老实说……什么都不会发生。"

# game/room.rpy:1227
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_7e05c898:

    # ermy_game "No one’s going to play this joke of a game, so I could as well just write a develop diary here."
    ermy_game "没人会想玩这个愚蠢的游戏，所以我也许在这儿开始写我的开发日记。"

# game/room.rpy:1228
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_b45014df:

    # ermy_game "It’s time to be fair with myself. I lack imagination to write anything at all."
    ermy_game "是该对自己诚实一点了。我完全没有想象力来写任何东西"

# game/room.rpy:1229
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_dd5652ba:

    # ermy_game "It’s… I mean, I wrote quite a lot, but it took me so much time… and, the truth is, it’s all worthless."
    ermy_game "就是……我的意思是，我曾经写了不少，可是花了很长时间……事实上，那些都没有价值。"

# game/room.rpy:1230
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_814b700c:

    # ermy_game "The characters don’t live. They’re made up. I’m made up myself. I don’t know what to write next, I really don’t know. My mind is totally empty, like a… jeez, I can’t even come up with a suitable description."
    ermy_game "人物不存在。他们是虚构的。我自己也是虚构的。我不知道该怎么继续写，我真不知道。我的脑海完全是空白的，仿佛……天哪，连合适的描述也想不出来。"

# game/room.rpy:1231
translate chinese ermy_game_d2_2c8600a7:

    # ermy_game "The plot, you say? It’s non-existing. It’s a cliché of a cliché of a cliché… Just like me. And you know what? That’s what people want. They don’t want my originality, but I fail even at copying things in a proper way."
    ermy_game "你说剧情？不存在的。这些是陈词滥调中的陈词滥调……就像我一样。你知道还有什么？这正好是人们所想要的。他们不想要我的独创性，可是甚至尽管模仿地好别人的东西我也是失败的。"

# game/room.rpy:1232
