    ee "索菲打着哆嗦不再说了。"

# game/room.rpy:652
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_a2c7abae:

    # ee "A cute girl, dressed in a maid outfit, joins the conversation. Where was she hiding? Weird… By the way, she holds a plushie in one hand."
    ee "一个穿着一套女仆服的漂亮的女孩儿加入对话。她以前在哪儿藏着呢？奇怪……再说，她手里拿着一个毛绒玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:663
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8d206a1b:

    # ee "Ring-ring…"
    ee "铃铃……"

# game/room.rpy:713
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d49564e5:

    # ee "I’m quite sure she’s referring to that plushie."
    ee "我很确定她指的是那个毛绒玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:723
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_91e9c136:

    # ee "And she was right."
    ee "原来，她是对的。"

# game/room.rpy:850
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_ca9491f8:

    # ee "So we did."
    ee "我们就谈了小猫。"

# game/room.rpy:927
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_8da00748:

    # ee "I too agreed with that. However, nothing happened."
    ee "我也同意了这句话，但是，什么都没发生。"

# game/room.rpy:931
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_7db20d8b:

    # ee "She moves so swiftly. It doesn’t even hurt… My vision starts to become blurry."
    ee "她迅速行动了。甚至都不疼。我的视力模糊了起来。"

# game/room.rpy:934
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_bf2f7a0d:

    # ee "Ring-ring. The phone rings again, but this time I manage to answer it, somehow."
    ee "铃铃。电话再次响起，但是这次我设法以某种方式接听电话。"

# game/room.rpy:935
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9ae1ae91:

    # ee "The guy on the other end of the line tells me that if I die, I’ll stay in this room forever. Uhm… why haven’t I thought about it before?"
    ee "打电话的那家伙跟我说要是我死亡，就会永远留在这个房间。哼……我怎么以前没想到这个呢？"

# game/room.rpy:936
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2b6f9836:

    # ee "I’m afraid it’s too late now."
    ee "恐怕现在已经太晚了。"

# game/room.rpy:940
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_761e2296:

    # ee "\"Love\""
    ee "\"爱情\""

# game/room.rpy:956
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0c7888ba:

    # ee "Two other girls appear right in front of my eyes."
    ee "两个其他的女孩子突然出现就在我眼前。"

# game/room.rpy:978
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_701124c6:

    # ee "Silence was her answer."
    ee "沉默是她的答案。"

# game/room.rpy:982
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2b75df09:

    # ee "She spanks me with her plushie."
    ee "她用她的玩具打我的屁股。"

# game/room.rpy:984
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_3f6c2965:

    # ee "I notice Sophie and Megan staring at me."
    ee "我发现索菲和梅根盯着我看。"

# game/room.rpy:1038
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_454940ca:

    # ee "She does a few quick swings, and shortly after that we’re the only ones standing in the room."
    ee "她快速摆了几步，不久之后，我们是唯一站在房间里的人。"

# game/room.rpy:1043
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_d47ffec2:

    # ee "I feel cold sweat dripping down my back. Sophie’s clearly bonkers, and I need to calm her down somehow."
    ee "我感觉到冷汗从我的背上流下来。索菲显然是傻子，我需要以某种方式使她平静下来。"

# game/room.rpy:1057
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_9e436be0:

    # ee "Swing! The needle bites me like a snake. My legs start to tremble."
    ee "针就像蛇一样咬了我。我的腿开始发抖。"

# game/room.rpy:1069
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_5a644da7:

    # ee "I’m back from the dead, it seems. Even more, the usual crowd’s here, as if nothing happened at all. The phone starts ringing again."
    ee "看来，我复活了。再说，那些老伙计也都在，似乎什么都没发生。电话又响起来了。"

# game/room.rpy:1070
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_0973f330:

    # ee "I don’t think I can get rid of that pain in my head, so I badly need to concentrate on something else… maybe small talk can help."
    ee "好像我不能摆脱头痛，所以我非常需要专注于其他东西……聊天也许能有帮助。"

# game/room.rpy:1078
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_2ec0ee81:

    # ee "You’re kidding me. Have they entirely forgotten about what happened before?"
    ee "你一定是开玩笑。她们难道把所有以前发生的事情都忘了吗？"

# game/room.rpy:1115
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_532099d4:

    # ee "Her annoyance doesn’t seem to be justified at the very slightest, but I’m not surprised, as it fits perfectly with the weird ambiance of that place."
    ee "她的生气看来一点道理也没有，我可不吃惊。它正好符合这个地方奇怪的气氛。"

# game/room.rpy:1142
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_740098a8:

    # s1 "You guys don’t even know about the right reason to hate everyone around you. I mean… they exist. They smell, they take space, they’re loud and annoying."
    s1 "你们甚至不知道恨周围每个人的正当理由。我是说……他们存在。他们呼吸、占用空间、他们吵到让人心烦"
# game/room.rpy:1143
translate chinese ermy_game_d1_aff9eaa8:

    # s1 "That’s why I always stay in my lab, so I could have some personal space. But even there, when I visit the bathroom, I look in the mirror and realize I’m no different."
    s1 "这就是为什么我一直呆在实验室里的原因，所以我可以有一些个人空间。但是即使在那儿，当我去洗手间时，我看着镜子，也意识到自己没有什么不同。"


# game/room.rpy:1308
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_553dedac:

    # imo "I can't believe you came empty-handed again."
    imo "我简直不敢相信你又空手来了。"

# game/room.rpy:1309
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_340597f8:

    # imo1 "That girl from yesterday came again, saying she needs to check on your progress."
    imo1 "昨天来过的那个女孩子今天又来了，说她需查一下你的进度。"

# game/room.rpy:1310
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_0a61f002:

    # imo "I replied that you can handle everything yourself."
    imo "我就跟她说你能够自己打理所有的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:1311
translate chinese sweet_home_d2_86347a80:

    # imo "By the way, what was in that document she gave you?"
    imo "顺便说一下，她给你的文件是什么内容？"

